        <scopecontent>
            <head>Collection Overview</head>

            <p>Minutes of meetings of stockholders and of directors, financial statements, account
                books, and other administrative documents of a firm manufacturing, converting, and
                distributing cotton fabrics, whose general office was located in St. Louis, Mo.
                Volumes have several identification numbers, the originals of which are marked with
                parentheses.</p>

